sentence-with-vars: What classes will I be able to take once I take department0 number0 ?
sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NAME FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 INNER JOIN COURSE_PREREQUISITE AS COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0 ON COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0.COURSE_ID INNER JOIN COURSE AS COURSEalias1 ON COURSEalias1.COURSE_ID = COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0.PRE_COURSE_ID WHERE COURSEalias1.DEPARTMENT = "MATH" AND COURSEalias1.NUMBER = 214 ;
